# E2E Test Fixtures

Generated by running tests with `E2E_RECORD=1 GITHUB_TOKEN=<token> bun test tests/e2e/`.

Do NOT edit manually. Regenerate by running the record command above.

## Files

- `models.json` - getModels() response snapshot
- `chat-completion.json` - Non-streaming chat completion response
- `chat-completion-stream.ndjson` - Streaming chat completion events
- `anthropic-message.json` - Non-streaming Anthropic message response
- `anthropic-stream.ndjson` - Streaming Anthropic message events
- `embeddings.json` - Embeddings API response
